# Parabolica Frontend Audit & Design System Report

This report summarizes the current visual state of the Parabolica Booking Terminal and Landing Page architecture. It groups existing patterns into 5 discrete "Design Sets" to guide all future development and ensure consistent spacing, typography, and responsiveness.

---

## 1. Global Visual Sets

We have identified 5 recurring design patterns that define the Parabolica "Human Building" / Brutalist aesthetic.

### Set 1: Cinematic Titan Headings
*   **Usage**: Hero sections, Chapter starts, Confirmation screens.
*   **Desktop Size**: `text-7xl` to `text-9xl` (often custom `text-[12rem]` for impact).
*   **Mobile Size**: `text-5xl` to `text-6xl`.
*   **Attributes**: `font-black`, `italic`, `tracking-tighter`, `uppercase`, `leading-[0.8]`.
*   **Key Files**: [landing-hero.tsx](file:///c:/Users/ZEEL/parabolica/ParabolicaWeb/components/sections/landing-hero.tsx), [booking/page.tsx](file:///c:/Users/ZEEL/parabolica/ParabolicaWeb/app/booking/page.tsx), `[deck]/page.tsx`.

### Set 2: Technical Serial Data (Mono)
*   **Usage**: Section counters, step indicators, technical metadata, labels.
*   **Desktop Size**: `text-[10px]` to `text-xs`.
*   **Attributes**: `font-mono`, `tracking-[0.5em]` to `tracking-[1em]`, `uppercase`, `text-white/40` or `#00ffd2`.
*   **Key Files**: [navbar.tsx](file:///c:/Users/ZEEL/parabolica/ParabolicaWeb/components/navbar.tsx), [booking/page.tsx](file:///c:/Users/ZEEL/parabolica/ParabolicaWeb/app/booking/page.tsx), [intro-sequence.tsx](file:///c:/Users/ZEEL/parabolica/ParabolicaWeb/components/intro-sequence.tsx).

### Set 3: Brutalist Module Cards
*   **Usage**: Selection grids, Configuration modules, Hardware displays.
*   **Structure**: `border border-white/10`, `bg-white/[0.02]`, `backdrop-blur-md`.
*   **Interaction**: `hover:border-[#00ffd2]`, `group-hover:translate-x-2`.
*   **Padding**: `p-8` (Mobile) to `p-24` (Desktop Hubs).
*   **Key Files**: [PrecisionCard](file:///c:/Users/ZEEL/parabolica/ParabolicaWeb/app/booking/page.tsx#407-416) (booking), [DeckExplorer](file:///c:/Users/ZEEL/parabolica/ParabolicaWeb/components/sections/deck-explorer.tsx#44-128) (home).

### Set 4: The Manifest (Body Text)
*   **Usage**: Descriptions, reviews, secondary info.
*   **Properties**: `text-sm` or `text-lg`, `font-light` to `font-bold`, `leading-relaxed`, `text-white/40`.
*   **Typography**: Mixes standard sans with monospace for "serial data" feel.

### Set 5: Mission Actions (Buttons)
*   **Type A (The Round Pulse)**: `rounded-full`, `bg-white`, `text-black`, `font-black italic`. Best for "Return to Reality" or "General CTA".
*   **Type B (The Brutalist Trigger)**: `border-2`, `bg-[#00ffd2]`, `text-black`, `font-black italic`, `tracking-widest`. Best for "Initialize Config" or "Finalize Mission".

