## 2. Spacing & Container Policy

*   **Page Gutter**: Standardized variable `--container-spacing` in [globals.css](file:///c:/Users/ZEEL/parabolica/ParabolicaWeb/app/globals.css) (scales from `1rem` to `5rem` based on breakpoint).
*   **Section Verticality**: `py-24` to `py-48`.
*   **Card Internal Gap**: `space-y-12` (Large titles) or `space-y-4` (Meta details).

