## 4. Observations & Inconsistencies

1.  **Title Weights**: Some older sections use `font-bold`, while the new Booking Terminal uses `font-black`. To maintain the "Premium" feel, I recommend moving all major headings to `font-black italic`.
2.  **Border Radius**: The site uses a mix of `rounded-full` (for landing buttons) and `rounded-none`/Sharp (for booking buttons). My report suggests keeping **Round for Home** and **Sharp for Terminal** to differentiate "Leisure" from "Operation".
3.  **Color Saturation**: `#00ffd2` is the heartbeat of the site. Ensure it is used sparingly as an accent to avoid visual fatigue.

---

## 5. Responsiveness Maturity

The site is currently **L90 Responsive**.
*   **The Grid System**: All 4-column layouts correctly collapse to 2-column or 1-column on mobile.
*   **Navigation**: The mobile menu in [navbar.tsx](file:///c:/Users/ZEEL/parabolica/ParabolicaWeb/components/navbar.tsx) is robust.
*   **Interaction**: Touch-hover states have been mitigated to prevent "stuck" hover effects.

**Recommendation**: No major code changes needed. Stick to the **Set 5** Sharp Button style for all future technical modules.
